{"tid":1542784,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【逆權運動】期指市場大混亂！昨炒撤回今中伏 券商：港交所出了事","createTime":"2019-09-05T03:25:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T03:25:54.000Z","uid":392,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5e6f6555514acb51222df9a804c30405dfd9c34b","tid":1542784,"uid":392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T03:25:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190905/large/1567652129_dc14.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190905%2Flarge%2F1567652129_dc14.jpg&h=fa873548&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n昨日港股喪炒撤回《逃犯條例》修訂消息而升近千點，有投資者趁消息炒一轉。不過今早有操作期指的投資者表示，未能進行期指買賣。<br />\n<br />\n有認購證發行商表示，期指市場今早出現問題，很多人交易不到，電腦不能落盤，成交全以人手操作。有交易商表示，今早9時30分過後，成交買賣速度很慢，相當不正常，交易量亦較平時少，差價亦很闊，指期交所連線有問題，平台亦連接不到。<br />\n有散戶投資者向記者表示，今早欲加注買期權，但平台像沒反應，難以交易。<br />\n<br />\n詳細報導:<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190905/60011269\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190905%2F60011269&d=Fy0o8YzXie14Yexn7W6rucyZng7V5AOcQmv89xdKlzQ%3D&h=bb31cc5e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190905%2F60011269&h=ab2be949\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190905/60011269</a><br />\n<br />\n攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8970e30e6750e8563b47ee7fbe121dde4ffcc5c6","tid":1542784,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T03:25:22.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</